 innych produkt\u00f3w piel\u0119gnacyjnych.<\/li>\n<li><b>Personalizowane wiadomo\u015bci:<\/b> Umie\u015b\u0107 w paczce kr\u00f3tki list dzi\u0119kuj\u0105cy za zakupy. Taki osobisty akcent mo\u017ce znacz\u0105co wp\u0142yn\u0105\u0107 na postrzeganie Twojej marki.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>Pami\u0119taj, \u017ce ma\u0142e gesty mog\u0105 przynie\u015b\u0107 du\u017ce korzy\u015bci. Zaskakuj\u0105c swoich klient\u00f3w, nie tylko zwi\u0119kszasz szans\u0119 na pozytywne recenzje, ale tak\u017ce budujesz lojalno\u015b\u0107 i d\u0142ugotrwa\u0142e relacje.<\/p>\n<p><b>Masz wi\u0119cej pyta\u0144? Skontaktuj si\u0119 z nami.<\/b><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<h1>Jak Zaskoczy\u0107 Klient\u00f3w w FBA: Nieszablonowe Pomys\u0142y na Dodatki<\/h1>\n<p>Czy kiedykolwiek zastana<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":6532,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"inline_featured_image":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[3],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-6531","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-kampanieppc"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/6531"}],"collection":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=6531"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/6531\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/6532"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=6531"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?pos